name: Intelligent Systems project: bike sharing service modeling
tagline: A university project on data analysis and modeling based on a bike sharing system data set.
body:
Models developed:
+ MLP based fitting
+ RBF based fitting
+ Fuzzy inference system
+ ANFIS
+ Time series forecasting based on NARX

Authors:
+ Alessio Villardita [villardita.alessio@gmail.com]
+ Sara Egidi [egidi.sara@gmail.com]

@ University of Pisa (unipi.it)
